Definition.WordDefinition: one time adv : on one occasion; "once I ran into her" [syn: {once}, {in one case}]

onetime adj : belonging to some prior time; "erstwhile friend"; "our former glory"; "the once capital of the state"; "her quondam lover" [syn: {erstwhile(a)}, {former(a)}, {once(a)}, {onetime(a)}, {quondam(a)}, {sometime(a)}]
